Restaurant - Paris

   Perfect matching foods and wines

   Between Opera and Madeleine, this beautiful property has a new owner
   since mid-2015 and new ambitions. Philippe Marques, who was (also) a
   decade sommelier Alain Senderens at Lucas Carton, works to make it the
   place to be in the capital for wine and its pairing with the dishes. At
   his side, Chef Thomas Moretto, passed by the Georges V, delivers a
   gourmet bistro cuisine. The harmony between food and wine is almost
   unlimited with almost 400 references of the divine bottle, over a dozen
   different peppers to better appreciate the subtleties.

Opening hours

   Monday - Friday

   12:00 - 14:30 / 19:00 - 22:30

   Saturday - Sunday

   Closed

Location

   8 rue Volney
   75002 Paris
   Star Wine List, Le guide des grands bars à vin et restaurants de vin à
   Paris.

